
CHANGELOG (qadrsc)

    Version 1.2.1 (2018-04-18)

        # Fixed the bug when trying to connect to a remote system with an at
          sign, but without username given (now raises an error).
        # Fixed the bug when trying to connect to a remote system without
          giving an username (now uses the name of current user, needed to be
          explicit before).

    Version 1.2.0 (2018-03-28)

        + Added the ability to also use remote paths as source.

        * Revised the code to parse remote paths (now done by a function).
        * Revised the usage information.

    Version 1.1.0 (2018-03-20)

        + Revised the command-line arguments as well as the code to parse them
          (now using common destination path syntax).
        * Revised the usage function in general.

    Version 1.0.1 (2018-02-21)

        # Fixed the empty source directory bug.

    Version 1.0.0 (2018-02-19)

        * First official release of this major version.
        
